how install Helm in kubernetes
we go us kubernetes ( ec2-ubuntu)
 
and go in site Helm
https://helm.sh/
and download Helm

press us tarminal this command
wget https://get.helm.sh/helm-v3.9.4-linux-amd64.tar.gz

now we extract file

tar -xf helm-v3.9.4-linux-amd64.tar.gz

now we check in us file if we have Helm

now we move it to /bin/

sudo mv helm /bin/

and press helm and check if work
